Cluster
Group where ECS tasks/services run. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Task Definition
Blueprint defining one or more containers + CPU/Mem + ports + roles. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Task
A running instance of the task definition containing one or more containers. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Container
The actual Docker workload running inside a task. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Service
Maintains desired number of tasks (replicas) and handles load balancing. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Task Set
A versioned group of tasks created during ECS Blue/Green deployments (original + replacement). [docs.aws.amazon.com]

AppSpec File (appspec.yml)
Deployment config telling CodeDeploy which Task Definition + container/port to use + optional hooks. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

TargetService
AppSpec section that points to the ECS Service + Task Definition revision. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

LoadBalancerInfo
Defines container name + port where ALB will route traffic during deployment. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Hooks
Optional Lambda functions executed at ECS lifecycle stages (BeforeInstall → AfterAllowTraffic). [docs.aws.amazon.com]

BeforeInstall
Runs before replacement task set is created. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

AfterInstall
Runs after replacement task set is created and attached to a target group. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

AfterAllowTestTraffic
Runs after ALB test listener sends traffic to the new task set. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

BeforeAllowTraffic
Runs before production traffic shifts to new task set. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

AfterAllowTraffic
Runs after production traffic starts flowing to replacement task set. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Blue/Green Deployment
CodeDeploy launches replacement task set → tests it → shifts traffic → terminates old one. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Traffic Shifting (CodeDeploy)
Controls how ALB moves traffic between original and replacement task sets. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Test Listener (ALB)
Sends traffic to replacement task set during validation stage. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Production Listener (ALB)
Handles live traffic and shifts it to the new task set upon approval. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Revision
In ECS deployments, the AppSpec file is considered the deployment revision. [docs.aws.amazon.com]

Lambda Validation Functions
Optional hooks that can approve/rollback deployments.


