IAM Roles (Task Role vs Execution Role)
Like Kubernetes service accounts, in ECS you have:
🟩 Task Role (app permissions)
Container uses this to access AWS services.
Example:

Access DynamoDB
Read/write S3
Read parameters from SSM

🟦 Execution Role (ECS agent permissions)
Used by ECS to:

Pull images from ECR
Fetch secrets
Push logs to CloudWatch
